author: stefan2
msg: Attache FS path & URL info to the working copy mergeinfo.
For now, only use that to get a log spanning not only the
branches but also the working copy.
As a side effect, this fixes an error condition where the
only branches found in m/i don't exist on HEAD anymore.
(mergeinfo_t): Add extra fields for url and FS path.
(get_urls): ... this and make it write the new mergeinfo_t fields.
(link_parents): Read the w/c info only once per mergeinfo_t instance.
(svn_min__common_parent): Make the common path span the w/c as well.
